snippet: A suicide bombing at a coffee shop in the northern city of Tripoli killed at least seven people and wounded more than 30 on Saturday.
abstract: At least seven people are killed and 30 more are wounded in suicide bombing in Tripoli, Lebanon; Nusra Front claims responsibility.
lead_paragraph: A suicide bombing at a coffee shop in the northern city of Tripoli killed at least seven people and wounded more than 30 on Saturday.

headline.main: Lebanon: Bombing Kills at Least 7 People at a Cafe
headline.print_headline: Lebanon: Bombing Kills at Least 7 People at a Cafe
